Text: RE fflPST will you pay martin for my part of that league too and you can mail a check to me at brompton or i can come pick it up from you doesnt matter take it easy Original Message From Bass Eric mailtoEric NRONcom Sent Monday January AM To Bryan Hull Subject RE ffl actually i forgot to take the out so Original Message From Bryan Hull mailto Sent Sunday January PM To Bass Eric Subject ffl Hey Bass whats up I hope you had a nice ChristmasNew Years So what does second place pay and what do I owe for that other league and I owe you for the Auburn LSU tickets and for Texas ending up higher in the polls than LSU Ill admit that bet was a lot closer than I thought it would be at the end of the season Geaux Tigers So let me know if I still have any money coming to me or if Im in the red Take it easy Bryan This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
